{"tid":2047021,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我呢排訓覺會好急尿，一晚要屙三到四次，有冇巴打可以救吓我","createTime":"2020-06-01T23:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T11:44:33.000Z","uid":318070,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8b6e2d435aba32d13d250d0252ac59943ebd3520","tid":2047021,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:14:37.000Z","msg":"呢兩三個禮拜，我只要訓兩三個鐘就會急尿急到扎醒<br />\n唔係心理感覺，係要屙十幾秒都未屙完，一晚仲要三四次<br />\n真係好折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要一扎醒起身嗰下口乾到個嘴好似就嚟爆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經試過訓覺之前兩個鐘唔飲水<br />\n但係都係咁急尿<br />\n都係會扎醒<br />\n有冇巴打知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：2x歲，冇咩不良嗜好，唔係咁鐘意飲酒，以前有食煙，但係戒咗好耐，打丁最多都係一日一次，唔吸毒"},{"pid":"a42948b1e91cd0a40e0b89b2b10d41fa05cd30f0","tid":2047021,"uid":65050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:20:47.000Z","msg":"睇醫生"},{"pid":"8804e18b651f6adaee4698a502380cd9435f2d71","tid":2047021,"uid":9489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:25:29.000Z","msg":"想搵連登醫生定搵爸打幫你含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dc642639d1ddeebf97faf157c1f488240c080f","tid":2047021,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:32:09.000Z","msg":"糖尿病？"},{"pid":"5f5931b48c12947df46c0cf12caa162868bfcf84","tid":2047021,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:33:11.000Z","msg":"一日一丁好多了"},{"pid":"a598a32191b7dceb2f42062dd03bd3a0abdb14e5","tid":2047021,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:33:57.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦仲諗<br />\n一係腎病一係內分泌失調"},{"pid":"fc34efe01a8fcc7c4f819235bee7d1bf222234d9","tid":2047021,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re