nt-urination%2Fpossible-causes&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=d25dbbaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://my.clevelandclinic.org/health/diseases/15533-urination--frequent-urination/possible-causes</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad13a3ac55ec086236624338cf5dcd7425b3fb9e","tid":2047021,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=2b2fe861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=a4cc2b3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n戒J 前後對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbbHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=2c0d214a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒"},{"pid":"3471637c8363ea66249c6015e3189686c58fe41b","tid":2047021,"uid":153679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f223b8bee0723a131405ea3e05d7310cb2a0e894","tid":2047021,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69dc642639d1ddeebf97faf157c1f488240c080f","tid":2047021,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:32:09.000Z","msg":"糖尿病？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:37:24.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔鍾意食甜野都會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"會 可能係遺傳"},{"pid":"5db52fec6ddca745997489498c966720d4155a01","tid":2047021,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"我初初畀男朋友含醒個陣都試過咁嘅情況"},{"pid":"257d7ad69805a1bc0bd1e346a02c19509c9d8f71","tid":2047021,"uid":275114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VN2N1g1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVN2N1g1.jpg&h=47646512&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07da37e97d2c989fca7beb7a8418f685fa99e745","tid":2047021,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc34efe01a8fcc7c4f819235bee7d1bf222234d9","tid":2047021,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T23:35:47.000Z","msg":"應該唔關打丁事 我小學打足十幾年日丁都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"Same here  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gi